ield field-name-field-chuvstva field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Чувства:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/grust&quot;&gt;Грусть&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/obida&quot;&gt;Обида&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/frustraciya&quot;&gt;Фрустрация&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
